data.description: Don't miss out on the incredible potential of this charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom ranch-style home! Featuring spacious rooms and situated on a fantastic lot, this property is a definite must-see. The framed and insulated basement offers even more possibilities with rough-ins for a potential third bathroom, providing ample space for expansion. Additionally, the garage comes equipped with a heater for added convenience. Conveniently located near schools and shopping, this home offers exceptional value that you won't want to let slip away. Schedule your viewing today before it's gone!
